### Professional Expense Tracker API Testing
### Make sure your Spring Boot app is running on localhost:8080

### 1. CREATE a new expense - Test DTO Transformation & 201 Status
POST http://localhost:8080/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Professional API Test",
  "amount": 25.99,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2024-10-14",
  "description": "Testing RequestDto → Entity → ResponseDto"
}

### 2. GET all expenses
GET http://localhost:8080/expenses

### 3. GET expense by ID (replace 1 with actual ID from database)
GET http://localhost:8080/expenses/1

### 4. GET expenses by category
GET http://localhost:8080/expenses/category/FOOD

### 5. GET expenses by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/expenses/date-range?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-12-31

### 6. UPDATE an expense (replace 1 with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/expenses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Grocery Shopping",
  "amount": 95.75,
  "category": "FOOD",
  "date": "2023-09-21"
}

### 7. GET total expense count
GET http://localhost:8080/expenses/count

### 8. GET expense count by category
GET http://localhost:8080/expenses/count/category/FOOD

### 9. GET expense count by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/expenses/count/date-range?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-12-31

### 10. DELETE an expense (replace 1 with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/expenses/1

